    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName> offre
                            al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110"
                                >Benevento</placeName> (prosegue l'elenco iniziato con il doc.
                            3535):</note></ab> <ab>(…) [42] Seu et <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Purchase">quod conparabimus</rs> in
                            <placeName ref="#places/3426"
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property"
                            >Ponticellum</placeName>, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">case</rs>
                        cum <rs key="#Curtes">curti</rs> sue, da <name ref="Egyptus">Egypto</name>
                        filius quoddam <name ref="Gaido">Gaiduni</name>, que est inter due <rs
                            key="#Roads">vię</rs>, una via que vadit ad Sanctum Marcum et alia via
                        que vadit ad <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/3420"
                            >Sanctum Valentinum</placeName>, <rs key="#Fines">per hec fines</rs>: de
                        capite fine rebus <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3401"
                            >Sancte Sophie</orgName>, de subtus fine ipso <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivo</rs>, in integrum <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                            Sancte Sophie</orgName> concessimus possidendum. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
